160
00:13:48,540 --> 00:13:50,930
You're his wife and you're a mother.

161
00:13:50,950 --> 00:13:53,200
So what?

162
00:13:53,210 --> 00:13:56,040
I can't use them as weapons.

163
00:13:56,040 --> 00:14:01,260
I don't want to use time I spent with him and my kids as weapons.

164
00:14:01,270 --> 00:14:04,940
It may be pathetic, but they're my pride and joy.

165
00:14:04,950 --> 00:14:06,440
Gwangbak,

166
